BUG: in filetype detection/setting, the following autocmds use `:set filetype=` rather than `:setfiletype`
filetypedetect  BufNewFile,BufRead
    *.hsc     set filetype=haskell
    *.bpk     set filetype=haskell
    *.hsig    set filetype=haskell
    *.bsv     set filetype=bsv
    lit.*cfg  set filetype=python
    *.ll      set filetype=llvm
    *.mlir    set filetype=mlir
    *.td      set filetype=tablegen
    *.v       set filetype=coq
